 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">A spherical lens can not be considered as a thin lens because the thickness is not negligible. In this work we present the deduction of the focal length equation for a spherical lens, developed through ray tracing technique. We compared the result with the focal length equation for thick lens obtained from matrix formalism. We also used the equation for a water sphere and compared with experimental data.</subfield>
